  "text": "The data reduction was carried out by R. Michel 2 using the IRAF 3 package and together with some home-made auxiliary Fortran programs and Awk scripts. All the images were bias subtracted and flat-field corrected (CCDRED). Cosmic rays were removed with the L.A. Cosmic 4 script van Dokkum (2001) [CITATION_1] .",
